{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We'd never heard of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's where we were, in Auschwitz, in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We look in the front us, we see four big chimneys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After we got disembarked, and we were marched towards the direction of the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't-- I didn't speak to my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't see anybody or remember anybody else speaking to anyone else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We just marched towards the place there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We figured, well-- you can imagine, we traveled for almost a week without food or water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We are so demoralized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You figure the sooner the end comes, the better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So you-- you won't have to suffer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I think this was the time when people really realized all these rumors, or the so-called rumors that we heard, are right in front of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were made-- we-- we were put in empty barracks, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and was a muddy floor, and walls and roof.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were made to undress and being told that we'd put our clothing in orderly fashion, tie our boots and shoes, and so we can find them easily when we come out.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everybody did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And un-- until today, I don't remember exchanging one word with my father or my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were made to go into a place where, right away, you could see there was something strange.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You see men and women naked in one-- in one place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Women cutting men's hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Men's cutting women's hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They weren't cutting the hair so much as tearing them out, because the clippers were dull.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were made to give everything up.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
